里布一起闲逛。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/film-reviews/dune-part-2-review-3593580">《沙丘：第二部分》评论：沙虫大小的续集应该会在票房上大吃一惊</a></strong></li></ul><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/robert-de-niro">罗伯特·德尼罗</a>、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/austin-butler">奥斯汀·巴特勒</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/snoop-dogg">史努比狗狗</a>齐聚这位说唱歌手的马里布私人庄园。</p><p>史努比狗狗 (Snoop Dogg) 的儿子科德尔 (Cordell) 在他的 Instagram 上发布了当晚的照片和视频，照片中明星们坐在一起，挥舞着和平手势，并与其他一些嘉宾聊天。</p><p> Instagram 帖子的标题还表明，这群明星云集的团体将一起享用私人晚餐。</p><p> Instagram 的标题是：“冠军德尼罗·埃尔维斯·斯库普。在马里布的房子里吃晚餐，谈论数字”。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/C5G4rOmPc6q/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.81